title: Eh-oh! Teletubbies are returning to our TV screens in HD - Wimbledon Guardian
text:
Tinky Winky, Dipsy, Laa-Laa and Po are ready to say "Eh-oh" to a new generation of children as Teletubbies returns. The colourful quartet still live over the hills and far away and have screens in their tummies which show short films.
 Wimbledon Guardian.
